    <title>Setup local kubernetes enviroment</title>
    <url>/posts/1975851450/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="setup-local-kubernetes-environment"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#setup-local-kubernetes-environment"></a> Setup local kubernetes environment</h1>
<blockquote>
<p>This article is about setting up local k8s environment for testing and learning k8s</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://markdown.diobrando0825.cn/2023-02-21-Screenshot%202023-02-21%20at%2012.18.41%20AM.png" alt="" /></p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="some-prerequisites"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#some-prerequisites"></a> Some prerequisites</h2>
<ul>
<li>Homebrew</li>
<li>Docker</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="install-minikube"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#install-minikube"></a> Install minikube</h2>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/">minikube</a> is local Kubernetes, focusing on making it easy to learn and develop for Kubernetes.</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Using homebrew to install minikube</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install minikube</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="start-minikube"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#start-minikube"></a> Start minikube</h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># By default the minikube will use docker to do the virtualization part</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># But you can also use other virtualization drivers</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># e.g. Hyperkit, VirtualBox https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/drivers/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># start command</span></span><br><span class="line">minikube start</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># you can also start in debug mode so that you can see more logs in the console</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># minikube start --v=7 --alsologtostderr</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="check-if-the-minikube-environment-is-created-successfully"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#check-if-the-minikube-environment-is-created-successfully"></a> Check if the minikube environment is created successfully</h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># check the status of the minikube</span></span><br><span class="line">❯ minikube status</span><br><span class="line">minikube</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">type</span>: Control Plane</span><br><span class="line">host: Running</span><br><span class="line">kubelet: Running</span><br><span class="line">apiserver: Running</span><br><span class="line">kubeconfig: Configured</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># check the nodes</span></span><br><span class="line">❯ kubectl get nodes</span><br><span class="line">NAME       STATUS   ROLES           AGE   VERSION</span><br><span class="line">minikube   Ready    control-plane   15s   v1.26.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="other-easy-access-online-environments"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#other-easy-access-online-environments"></a> Other easy access online environments</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://killercoda.com/">killercoda</a></li>
</ul>
<p>…</p>
<h2 id="deployment"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#deployment"></a> Deployment</h2>
<h3 id="create-deploymentyaml"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#create-deploymentyaml"></a> Create deployment.yaml</h3>
<p>I strongly recommend you to use vscode’s k8s extension, it will help you to create the yaml file by providing some templates.</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">apps/v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">testapp</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">replicas:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">selector:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">matchLabels:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">app:</span> <span class="string">testapp</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">template:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">labels:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">app:</span> <span class="string">testapp</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">containers:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">testapp</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">&lt;image&gt;</span> <span class="comment"># change this to your image</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">resources:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">limits:</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">memory:</span> <span class="string">&quot;128Mi&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">cpu:</span> <span class="string">&quot;500m&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">containerPort:</span> <span class="number">5000</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># NodePort service</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">Service</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">testapp-service</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">selector:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">app:</span> <span class="string">testapp</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">NodePort</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">port:</span> <span class="number">5000</span> <span class="comment"># internal port</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">targetPort:</span> <span class="number">30800</span> <span class="comment"># this is the port exposed outside the container</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="apply-the-deployment"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#apply-the-deployment"></a> Apply the deployment</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">❯ kubectl apply -f delpoyment.yaml</span><br><span class="line">deployment.apps/testapp created</span><br><span class="line">service/testapp-service created</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="check-the-deployment"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#check-the-deployment"></a> Check the deployment</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">❯ kubectl get services</span><br><span class="line">NAME              TYPE        CLUSTER-IP       EXTERNAL-IP   PORT(S)    AGE</span><br><span class="line">kubernetes        ClusterIP   10.96.0.1        &lt;none&gt;        443/TCP    12h</span><br><span class="line">testapp-service   ClusterIP   10.105.137.213   &lt;none&gt;        5000/TCP   4m42s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="access-the-service"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#access-the-service"></a> Access the service</h3>
<p>For this step, because we are using minikube, we need to use the <code>minikube service</code> command to access the service.</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">❯ minikube service testapp-service</span><br><span class="line">|-----------|-----------------|-------------|---------------------------|</span><br><span class="line">| NAMESPACE |      NAME       | TARGET PORT |            URL            |</span><br><span class="line">|-----------|-----------------|-------------|---------------------------|</span><br><span class="line">| default   | testapp-service |        5000 | http://192.168.49.2:30625 |</span><br><span class="line">|-----------|-----------------|-------------|---------------------------|</span><br><span class="line">🏃  Starting tunnel <span class="keyword">for</span> service testapp-service.</span><br><span class="line">|-----------|-----------------|-------------|------------------------|</span><br><span class="line">| NAMESPACE |      NAME       | TARGET PORT |          URL           |</span><br><span class="line">|-----------|-----------------|-------------|------------------------|</span><br><span class="line">| default   | testapp-service |             | http://127.0.0.1:51764 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="delete-the-deployment"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#delete-the-deployment"></a> Delete the deployment</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">❯ kubectl delete -f deployment.yaml</span><br><span class="line">deployment.apps <span class="string">&quot;testapp&quot;</span> deleted</span><br><span class="line">service <span class="string">&quot;testapp-service&quot;</span> deleted</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="reference"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#reference"></a> Reference</h1>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/">minikube docs</a></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
